<title>zhǔ wǒ men shēn shēn de zhī dào 迦南56</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ men shēn shēn de zhī dào zài měi yī gè shí kè lǐ
 nǐ de ài cóng lái cóng lái jiù méi yǒu jiǎn qù
 zhǔ wǒ men shēn shēn de zhī dào zài měi yī gè shí kè lǐ
 wǒ men wéi yī de tóng bàn jiù shì nǐ
 wǒ men de xīn chī qíng de xiàng wǎng nǐ
 wǒ men de xīn chī qíng de zhuī suí nǐ
 yīn wèi nǐ shì qiān wàn rén zhōng de dì yī rén
 méi yǒu shén me néng hé nǐ xiāng bǐ</lyrics>
</song>